{"tid":1703300,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【Now新聞台】本台記者被催淚彈擊中左手臂受傷","createTime":"2019-11-10T08:16:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T08:28:43.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9fb58abbd38db0b7714be382971f886c6df0caf4","tid":1703300,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T08:16:48.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】荃灣有示威者破壞商舖及堵路，防暴警察趕到驅趕。有防暴向天橋上施放催淚彈，擊中本台記者左手臂。<br />\n<br />\n一班防暴警察離開荃新天地時，有警員從行駛中的警車內向行人天橋施放催淚彈，一枚催淚彈擊中本台記者，她的左手手臂燒傷，即傷接受急救員治理。<br />\n<br />\n而較早前一批示威者在荃灣廣場破壞一間連鎖咖啡店，隨即離開，走到附近沙咀道堵路，之後快閃離開。防暴警察趕到，示威者四散。有人被捕，被帶上警車。<br />\n<br />\n防暴警察又在荃新天地附近拘捕一名男子，即場搜查他的隨身物品。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=369366\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D369366&d=Fs4PzESj5DMZecC7Kr%2FqWEbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=0169c055\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D369366&h=84c9c2cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=369366</a>"},{"pid":"4d7f67f33b1babc2ecd152d5ea138434d57285e1","tid":1703300,"uid":248098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T08:19:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇人性㗎女人都射，人哋女仔黎架隻手花左以後點見人"},{"pid":"69071c15db25510a011808f0b687b6e71408e3a5","tid":1703300,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d7f67f33b1babc2ecd152d5ea138434d57285e1","tid":1703300,"uid":248098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T08:19:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇人性㗎女人都射，人哋女仔黎架隻手花左以後點見人"},"citedBy":0,"replyT